{"type":"message","id":"9786894a","parentId":"d49afa7b","timestamp":"2026-03-06T14:55:51.093Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"  **Listing available tools**[[reply_to_current]] Based on my system prompt, here are the tools available in this runtime:\n\n1. **message** — Send, delete, and manage messages via channel plugins\n   - Actions: send, broadcast\n   - Supports: Feishu, Telegram, Discord, etc.\n\n2. **sessions_list** — List sessions with optional filters and last messages\n\n3. **sessions_history** — Fetch message history for a session\n\n4. **sessions_send** — Send a message into another session\n\n5. **session_status** — Show session status card (usage + time + cost)\n\n**Notable:** No `read`, `exec`, or `feishu_doc` tools are exposed in this runtime.\n\nThat's why I can't directly read files or run the extract-chat.js script. I need either:\n- The skill file contents pasted here, or\n- The draft content pasted here"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"xunfei","model":"xopkimik25","usage":{"input":50640,"output":187,"cacheRead":8,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":50835,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772808917905}}
